ISysComponent, ISysDevelopmentLogSwitch, ISysGlobal, ISysLogConstants, ISysService
public final class CSysPropertyService
extends ASysSimpleService

This Service retrieves the System properties of the Host and returns it as ISysTable. Setting Properties works on System.properties. Example for CSysPropertyTable.

COMMAND getProperty
